                "text": "As a move action, a green rageshkor can align portions of the flexible frill of its back armor to block attacks from one enemy the rageshkor is observing. Doing so increases the rageshkor\u2019s AC by 2 against attacks from that enemy until the start of the rageshkor\u2019s next turn.",
